videos.description: Following a convincing win over Ole Miss, Kobe Brown says "every little detail matters" when it comes to progressing in the SEC Tournament.
videos.headline: Brown says Missouri must make everything count

videos.description: Cuonzo Martin tells SEC Now of the gritty defense Missouri played in the 72-60 tournament win over Ole Miss: "It's got to be within your soul."
videos.headline: Martin stresses the importance of defense for Mizzou

videos.description: Missouri sets the tone with a strong second-half run to defeat Ole Miss, xx-xx, in the first round of the SEC Tournament.
videos.headline: 12-seed Mizzou skates by 13-seed Rebels in SEC tourney
